Annual Report on Form 10-K for the fiscal year ended December 31, 2004 or such subsidiaries as are not required to be listed in such Exhibit pursuant to Item 601(b)(21)(ii) of Regulation S-K.
Incorporation and Good Standing of the Company and its Subsidiaries
 
