will be required to instruct the Trustee to determine the Trading Price of the Securities beginning on the next Trading Day and on each successive Trading Day until the Trading Price per $1,000 original principal amount of Securities is greater than or equal to 98% of the product of the Closing Price of the Company's Common Stock and the current Conversion Rate of the Securities.
 
