Barnes Aerospace operating margin  19.0% to 20.0%, slightly up from 18.9% in 2007 and including approximately $3 million of expenses related to the Ogden facility expansion. Recently announced delays of the Boeing 787 have been considered in Barnes Aerospaces 2008 outlook.
Barnes Distribution operating margin  8.0%; up from 1.8% in 2007.
Barnes Industrial operating margin  approximately 14.0%, in-line with the 2007 level.
Tax rate  approximately 23% to 25%, an increase over the 2007 rate primarily due to improved financial performance within Distribution.
