Barnes Group Inc. (NYSE:B) is an international aerospace and industrial components manufacturer and full-service distribution company focused on achieving consistent, sustainable, and predictable results.  Founded in 1857, Barnes Group consists of three businesses:  Barnes Aerospace, Barnes Distribution and Barnes Industrial.  More than 6,400 dedicated employees at more than 70 locations worldwide contribute to Barnes Group Inc.s success.  For more information, visit .
