Barnes Group Inc. (NYSE:B) is a diversified global manufacturer and logistical services company focused on providing precision component manufacturing and operating service support.  Founded in 1857, the 5,600 dedicated employees at more than 70 locations worldwide are committed to achieving consistent and sustainable profitable growth.  For more information, visit .  Barnes Group, the Critical Components People.
