Barnes Group Inc. (the "Company") issued a press release on July 16, 2012 announcing that it has entered into a definitive agreement to acquire Synventive Molding Solutions, a leading designer and manufacturer of highly engineered and customized hot runner systems, components, and services. A copy of the press release is furnished with this report as Exhibit 99.1.  
