(k)    None of the Company or the Company Subsidiaries (i) has been a member of an affiliated, consolidated, combined or unitary group (or similar group under state, local or foreign Law) other than a group consisting only of the Company and the Company Subsidiaries, or (ii) has liability for the Taxes of any Person (other than the Company and the Company Subsidiaries) under Treasury Regulations Section 1.1502-6 (or any similar provision of state, local or foreign Law), as a transferee or successor, by contract or otherwise.
