(d)        Election of Directors.
On December 14, 2012, the Board of Directors (the "Board") of Barnes Group Inc. (the "Company") elected Francis J. Kramer as an independent director of the Company, effective immediately, for a term ending on the date of the 2013 Annual Meeting of Stockholders.
 
There is no arrangement or understanding between Mr. Kramer and any other persons by which he was selected as a director. Additionally, there are no transactions involving Mr. Kramer requiring disclosure under Item 404(a) of Regulation S-K.
